Use iKaaro M13
---------------

python = Python-2.4.1.tgz
itools = itools--main--0.8--patch-102.tgz
iKaaro = ikaaro--main--0.13--patch-104.tgz
iHotfix = iHotfix--main--0.5--patch-9.tgz

Install mysql python module
-----------------------------

$ cd Python-2.4.1/lib/python2.4/site-packages/
$ ln -s /usr/lib/python2.4/site-packages/MySQLdb
$ ln -s /usr/lib/python2.4/site-packages/_mysql*.py .
$ ln -s /usr/lib/python2.4/site-packages/_mysql*.so .


Data.fs
---------

the admin: passwd -> Scrib-2005*

Update
-------

To update a Data.fs from culutre--xxx--0.4 to culture--xxx--0.5
go to 
http://localhost:8080/scrib/manage_ikaaro
and click on update button.

